To run this project:

1. remove the pox directory from your mininet installation 
2. clone the repo and move the pox directory to where the one you deleted was 
3. run finaltopo.sh to start mininet
4. run startpox.sh to start the pox controller 
5. rules for blocking traffic are in date_time.txt, firewall.txt, usage_caps.txt

date_time.txt format 
    - srcmac destman startdate enddate (date format is year month day hour minute)

firewall.txt format 
    - srcmac destman (true / false)

usage_caps.txt format 
    - srcmac destmac bitcap (bytes)

